were 300,000 years old. But the description of coynes given by GDW\'s "Droyne"
alien module seem to say they were a recent invention. Clearly, there is
a contradiction here.

Mark Miller, in an interview in the Digest, mentioned the appearance of
the Major Races on the coynes as a mystery remaining to be solved. (I\'d
love to hear his views on all this!)  This statement seems to contradict the
tidy explanation given in the alien module (no mystery there.)

>>
