>They are as far away from Sylea as Terra is, and yet they were being
>colonized 60 years after the founding of the Imperium. It wasn\'t until
>four centuries later that Terra was absorbed.

Because they were mostly undeveloped.  I see no evidence that coloniztion
was driven by anything more than lack of opportunities elsewhere.


