     You still get the sentient machines and vampire fleets, but they end up
     being a rare occurrence instead of part of some bloody great Cthuloid
     conspiracy... "I\'ve seen jumpspace - and it\'s ALIVE!!!!"  Ner ner ner
     ner... whoo baby.
