Hi Tom, this is Rob, a fellow CT fan.

There is a method for doing this, but it uses the Striker rules for
vehicle combat, not the Book 4 rules. The rules are detailed in an
appendix called "Integration with High Guard" in Book 2 of Striker. (The
vehicle combat rules themselves are detailed in Striker-Book1.)

If you like CT Book 4, I strongly recommend you get hold of a copy of
the original Striker boxed set. It has wargame statistics for all the
weapons from Mercenary in it. Plus compatability rules for CT.

