	Some things to note:

Striker Combat between starships is a very different animal than regular
starship combat with Book-2 or High Guard rules. Just about every hit
with a beam or pulse laser will result in Critical damage, and turns are
30 seconds long instead of ~20 minutes.

This shouldn\'t be too surprising since Striker combat ranges are on the
order of 10 to 100 km, whereas CT Book-2 ranges are on the order of
100,000 to 1,000,000 km.

This makes Striker starship combat far more brief and more exciting than
the normal style at long distances. Something to keep in mind when you
close on a vessal to board it...	8^)

