> Phil, you finally have come up with some reasonable, responsible posts!
> Thank You!
>
> As for the Computing Power, I developed a system of formulae for doing
> non-standard computers for traveller craft under FF&S; I don\'t have them
> handy, but the basic conversion point for FF&S is the Crew Multiplier;
