Actually, so do I! And I\'ve worked my own assumptions to handle it in modified
Traveller background that I use, but which wouldn\'t work for anyone else who
wasn\'t prepared to accept the assumptions of my alternate Imperial History
and related technology. It works quite well ... and you can have ships that
have no crew or few crew ... and which have no Bridges, only individual VR
control pods that are carefully dispersed and armoured such that one hit on
the "bridge" cannot KO the ship.

> However, I agree on your basic premise; Each TL should have a computer
> table, with all the models available at that TL.

*Exactly* this is *just* what there should be available ... so that you *can*
