    'year' => 1996,
    'from' => 'sdollar@goodnet.com',
    'topic' => 'K\'Kree',
    'body' => 'Hello all!

I\'m having hell finding any sort of information on the K\'kree.

I finally found an old Megatraveller Digest (DGP) that gave some
basic background on them, but I\'m desperately trying to find some
Character Generation rules for CT/MT for them.

I know that Traveller Alien Module 2 is THE canon on them, but I
can\'t find a copy of it anywhere...

If anyone has a copy they would be willing to part with, I\'d be
willing to pay a reasonable price.  If not, I\'d sure like to get
a hold of the character generation data for them, if for no other
