MegaTraveller Encyclopedia entry "Nth Interstellar War" (p. 33), is that
the initial wars between the Solomani and the Vilani were fought on the
Vilani side with only the resources of the local Imperial Governor (this
is a direct steal from the GDW boardgame Imperium), allowing the
Solomani to win against limited opposition.  By the time the central
government had noticed what was going on and dispatched major fleet
units (after the Terran victory in the 8th Interstellar War), the Terrans
had invented J-3 (which the Vilani did not have) and generally kicked
Imperial behind.

