were hinted at already in the \'Referee\'s Gaming Kit\' and later in =
\'Knightfall\'. These aliens was a psionically and tecnologically very =
advanced race that lived before the Ancients. The Ancients studied them =
extensively, but apparently they just left the (known) universe long =
before the rise of the Ancients.

It was part of DGP\'s plan that they should return to charted space in =
the middle of the Rebellion, being such a threat to all sentient races =
that not only would the different factions of the Rebellion, but all =
sentient races, have to band together to defeat them.

This and much more was disclosed in the MegaTraveller Journal #4, =
because with the advent of TNE, nothing would ever come of it.

