> view that every comment in this thread has to either argue that the
> plague is cannon, exactly as written, or that it has be to abondoned
> altogether, that\'s just too bad.

Is it arrogance to point out that the event in question, regardless of whether
it is canon or not, occurred *after* the Vilani collapse makes your point that
it is an explanation for said collapse wrong? I would have though not! Be as
sarcastic as you want, doesn\'t worry me that your point is a) not reasonable
(because it goes against the "facts" as known as to the date of appearance) and
b) therefore cannot be used as an explanation for the Terran victory. If you
don\'t see that, or if you think that it\'s arrogant of me to point it out, fine,
I can live with it ... but it may be better if we exchange views directly
without bothering the mailing list with any further rancour that may result
from this. Or we can simply agree to disagree. I can live with either. Your
ball.

Phil McGregor

